; Throne (تخت) — 01_CORE_MECHANICS.md §5
; status: calibrated — max_hp=2000 is feel-reasoned (2-3 min focused fire for a small
;   army per session-9 DPS math). Win-condition live-test pending; retune after AI-vs-AI.
; Capital building. Pre-placed. Loss = defeat. Spawns workers.
; High HP — destroying it ends the match; must require sustained effort.
; No farr_per_tick — Throne is not a Farr generator.
