; Khaneh (house) — 01_CORE_MECHANICS.md §5
; status: calibrated — max_hp=200 live-tested session-9 (~20s for solo piyade, felt right).
;   population_capacity=5 anchored to spec (01_CORE_MECHANICS.md §5, §9.L1 session-6 revert).
;   construction_ticks=90 is a placeholder (3s — originally a dwell-skeleton value).
; Population cap +10 per building (placeholder starting point — spec says +5;
; Phase 3 session 1 wave 1C kickoff opted for +10 to give workers more
; headroom while production queues are pending session 2; balance-engineer
; retunes after first playtest). "50 coin" per spec.
; Low HP — not a combat building.
; construction_ticks lands here for session 2's progress-bar wiring; session
; 1's placement skeleton uses a smaller dwell value (90 ticks = ~3s at 30Hz)
; via UnitState_Constructing's KHANEH_DWELL_TICKS — Khaneh appears INSTANTLY
; on arrival in session 1 per the wave 1C kickoff (no in-progress state yet).
[sub_resource type="Resource" id="bldg_khaneh"]
script = ExtResource("3_bldgstats")
