; =========================================================================
; FogConfig sub-resource
; =========================================================================
; status: anchored — all sight radii derived from FOG_DATA_CONTRACT.md §2.2
;   canonical table. §9.L1 spec-wins at Wave 3A.0 overrode brief's inflated
;   values (documented in comments below). Should only change if FOG_DATA_CONTRACT
;   §2.2 changes. Sowari-khaneh/Tirandazi=2 cells is balance-engineer discretion
;   (table gap) but treated as anchored for consistency with the §2.2 pattern.
; Values from FOG_DATA_CONTRACT.md §2.2 sight-radius table.
; All sight radii are integer cell counts at 4m/cell.
;
; §9.L1 spec-wins: Brief suggested Kargar=4, Piyade=5, Kamandar=6, Savar=6,
; mounted=7. FOG_DATA_CONTRACT §2.2 canonical table specifies Kargar=3,
; Piyade=3, Kamandar=4, Savar=4, Rostam=5, Throne=4. Spec overrides brief.
;
; Sowari-khaneh=2, Tirandazi=2: NOT in §2.2 table (table lists only named
; buildings). Set to 2 cells (parity with Atashkadeh's compact sacral footprint)
; — additive, non-overriding. Balance-engineer discretion per brief §4.
;
; Khaneh=0, Mazra'eh=0, Ma'dan=0: footprint-only per brief §4 (non-military
; buildings reveal only their built footprint, no surrounding radius at 3A.0).
;
; cell_size_meters=4.0 per FOG_DATA_CONTRACT §1.1 (2× WorldGrid.CELL_SIZE).
;
; H3 dormant-schema first-exercise: field ships dormant at Wave 3A.0.
; Wave 3A.5 consumers (7 building _on_placement_complete hooks) read these
; values for register_vision_source calls.
;
; §9.L6 forward-compat-guard-sweep result (at Wave 3A.0 ship time):
;   git grep -n 'fog_config\|BalanceData\.fog' game/scripts/ → ZERO readers.
;   Only consumer-side readers confirmed absent: all 3A.5 call-sites deferred.
;   L8/L9 apply at 3A.5 debug-overlay time — no UI surface at 3A.0.

[sub_resource type="Resource" id="fog_cfg"]
script = ExtResource("9_fogconfig")
cell_size_meters = 4.0
sight_kargar_cells = 3
sight_piyade_cells = 3
sight_kamandar_cells = 4
sight_savar_cells = 4
sight_rostam_cells = 5
sight_throne_cells = 4
sight_sarbazkhane_cells = 3
sight_atashkadeh_cells = 2
sight_sowari_khaneh_cells = 2
sight_tirandazi_cells = 2
sight_khaneh_cells = 0
sight_mazraeh_cells = 0
sight_madan_cells = 0

